{
  "content": "<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How does Quebec business funding work?</h2>\n              <div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                  Quebec operates one of Canada's most comprehensive and generous business funding\n                  ecosystems with over $1.8 billion available annually. The province's unique economic\n                  development approach combines substantial direct grants, world-leading R&D tax credits,\n                  and strategic sector investments through Investissement Québec.\n                </p>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                  Quebec's R&D tax credit system is particularly notable, offering combined federal-provincial\n                  credits that can exceed 55% of eligible expenditures—among the highest in North America.\n                  The province also maintains strong support for francophone businesses, cultural industries,\n                  and companies contributing to Quebec's economic sovereignty.\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4 my-6\">\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                    <strong>Key Insight:</strong> Quebec's funding programs strongly favor businesses that\n                    contribute to the provincial economy through job creation, technology development, or\n                    export activities. French-language applications are processed in the same manner as\n                    English, and bilingual support is widely available.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12\">What are the major Quebec grant programs?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\">\n                {/* Investissement Quebec SME Fund */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Investissement Québec SME Fund</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Up to $10M</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Growth Capital</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Quebec's primary economic development agency offers comprehensive financing\n                      solutions including loans, loan guarantees, and equity investments for SMEs.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Flexible loan structures</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Equity investment options</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Strategic advisory services</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* Quebec R&D Tax Credits */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Quebec R&D Tax Credits (37.5%)</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>37.5% Credit</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Refundable</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      One of North America's most generous R&D incentives. Quebec's refundable\n                      tax credit can return up to 37.5% of eligible R&D salary expenditures.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Fully refundable for CCPCs</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Stacks with federal SR&ED</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Combined rate can exceed 55%</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* Quebec Startup Fund */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Quebec Startup Fund (Fonds de démarrage)</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>$50K - $200K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Venture Capital</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Early-stage venture capital for innovative Quebec startups with high\n                      growth potential. Includes mentorship and network access.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Seed and pre-seed funding</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Mentorship programs</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Follow-on investment options</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                {/* PME MTL */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">PME MTL (Montreal Economic Development)</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>$5K - $50K</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span><strong>Montreal</strong></span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-4\">\n                      Montreal's network of economic development agencies offers grants,\n                      technical assistance, and business support across all 19 boroughs.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Startup grants</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Technical assistance</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-center\">\n                        <span>Interest-free loans</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Who is Eligible for Quebec Business Grants?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                Quebec business grants are available to for-profit enterprises operating within Quebec.\n                Most programs require Quebec incorporation or significant provincial operations. R&D\n                tax credits are available to any corporation conducting eligible R&D activities in Quebec.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Generally Eligible\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Incorporated in Quebec (provincially or federally registered)</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>SMEs with significant Quebec operations</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Businesses creating Quebec jobs</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Companies with growth or export plans</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Good standing with Revenu Québec</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Generally Ineligible\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Businesses without Quebec presence</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Projects completed before application</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Businesses in tax arrears with Revenu Québec</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Real estate speculation</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Retail without innovation component</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Much Grant Funding Can Quebec Businesses Get?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                Quebec offers some of Canada's most generous funding levels. Grant amounts\n                vary by program, but the province's R&D tax credits provide ongoing,\n                substantial returns on innovation investments.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-blue-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Program Type</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Typical Range</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Notes</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">R&D Tax Credits</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">Up to 37.5%</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Of eligible salaries</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Investissement Québec</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">$100K - $10M</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Loans/equity</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Startup Programs</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">$50K - $200K</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Equity investment</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Municipal Programs (PME MTL)</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-green-600\">$5K - $50K</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Grants/loans</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Quebec's R&D tax credit combined with federal SR&ED can\n                  return over 55% of eligible R&D expenditures. This makes Quebec one of the most\n                  attractive jurisdictions in North America for R&D-intensive companies.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How to Apply for Quebec Business Grants - Step by Step</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-6\">\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">1</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Research Programs (1-2 weeks)</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Visit Investissement Québec's website, Quebec.ca business portal, and\n                      municipal economic development offices. Many programs require pre-approval\n                      before starting your project.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">2</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Initial Consultation</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Investissement Québec offers free business consultations. For R&D credits,\n                      consult with a SR&ED specialist before year-end to ensure proper documentation.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">3</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Prepare Application (2-4 weeks)</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Quebec applications typically require business plans, financial projections,\n                      project descriptions, and impact assessments. French and English are accepted.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">4</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Submit & Due Diligence</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Submit applications through official portals. Larger projects undergo\n                      financial and technical due diligence. Processing typically takes 45-90 days.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">5</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Agreement & Disbursement</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Upon approval, sign a contribution agreement. Quebec typically uses\n                      milestone-based or reimbursement funding models with regular reporting.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What Documents Are Required for Quebec Grant Applications?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center\">\n                    Core Business Documents\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>NEQ (Numéro d'entreprise du Québec)</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>2-3 years of audited financial statements</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Current year-to-date financials</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Shareholder/ownership documentation</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center\">\n                    Project-Specific Documents\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Detailed project plan with milestones</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Budget with vendor quotes</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Job creation projections</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Market analysis (for startups)</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Long Does Quebec Grant Approval Take?</h2>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-blue-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Program Type</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Review Timeline</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">First Payment</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">R&D Tax Credits</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">60-90 days after filing</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">With tax refund</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Investissement Québec</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">45-90 days</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Upon closing</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Municipal Programs</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">30-60 days</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Milestone basis</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Note:</strong> R&D tax credits are claimed with your annual corporate tax\n                  return. To receive credits faster, plan your tax filing strategically and ensure\n                  all documentation is complete.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Common Mistakes to Avoid with Quebec Grant Applications</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">1</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Missing R&D Documentation</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Quebec's R&D credits require contemporaneous documentation of\n                          technological uncertainties and systematic investigation. Retroactive\n                          documentation often results in reduced claims or audits.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">2</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Starting Projects Before Approval</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Many Quebec grant programs require pre-approval before project\n                          commencement. Costs incurred before approval are typically ineligible.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">3</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Underestimating Quebec Job Impact</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Quebec programs strongly favor job creation within the province.\n                          Applications should clearly demonstrate how funding will lead to\n                          high-quality Quebec employment.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Which industries get the most Quebec funding?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">AI & Technology</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Montreal AI ecosystem, Scale AI, MILA partnerships</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Clean Technology</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Hydroelectricity, batteries, sustainable tech</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Aerospace</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Third-largest aerospace hub globally</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Life Sciences</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Pharma, biotech, medical devices</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Video Games & VFX</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Major studios, strong tax credits</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Cultural Industries</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Film, music, publishing, media</p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Are there local grants in Montreal and Quebec City?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Montreal / Montréal</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>PME MTL – 19 borough offices</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Montréal International – FDI support</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Centech, District 3 – Accelerators</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>MILA – AI research partnerships</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Quebec City / Ville de Québec</h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Québec International – Regional development</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>CDEC programs – Local grants</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Laval Technopole – Tech hub support</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What if I don't qualify for Quebec grants?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">Federal SR&ED</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    Federal R&D tax credits stack with Quebec credits for combined returns\n                    exceeding 55% of eligible expenditures.\n                  </p>\n                  <a href=\"/blog/sred-scientific-research-experimental-development\">\n                    Learn about SR&ED →\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">CED-Q (Federal)</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    Canada Economic Development for Quebec Regions offers federal funding\n                    that complements provincial programs.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                {faqData.map((faq, index) => (\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg flex items-start\">\n                        {faq.question}\n                      </h3>\n                      <p class=\"text-gray-700 mt-2 ml-7\">{faq.answer}</p>\n                  </div>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n",
  "shortAnswer": "Yes — Complete guide to Quebec small business grants. Access Investissement Québec SME Fund, Quebec Startup Fund, R&D Tax Credits up to 37.5%, and francophone business support. Funding available: up to $1.8B+.",
  "shortAnswerQuestion": "What small business grants are available in 2026?",
  "faq": [
    {
      "question": "What is the application deadline for Quebec Small Business Grants  | .8B+ Quebec SME Funding in 2026?",
      "answer": "Deadlines typically vary by specific program tier. However, for 2026, many initiatives operate on a rolling intake basis until funds are depleted. Check the official portal for specific cutoffs."
    },
    {
      "question": "How much funding can I get through Quebec Small Business Grants  | .8B+ Quebec SME Funding?",
      "answer": "Funding amounts range depending on business size and scope. Top awards can reach $1."
    },
